\id 1SA - Havai
\h 1 Samuel
\toc1 1 Samuel
\toc2 1 Samuel
\toc3 1 SA
\mt1 1 Samuel
\c 3
\s1 Samuel
\p 
\v 19 Me siu Samuel mo lawua, me \nd Huqe\nd* mo tino meie. \nd Huqe\nd* he siregi na leo noi Samuel tea vena soi talo tano.
\v 20 Me doluegi Israel tavuigi Dan mo dadari Bereseba ngere rau ilo ve \nd Huqe\nd* mo rivu Samuel mwere na nona tangaloi ligoligogi.
\v 21 Me \nd Huqe\nd* mo vomai tuqaravu lo Saelo, huri mo vosangie lawe Samuel lo Saelo duruhi na nona leo.
\c 7
\s1 Samuel u Vevegi Nire tau Israel
\p 
\v 15 Samuel u voragi na tangaloi vevegi lolo Israel lolo rani doluegi hinge u mwaso lolona.
\v 16 Vataha na higao mo dige lategi mo dali mo vano Betel mo vano Kilkal me Misba, mo vevegi nire tau Israel lolo ute ngere hi doluegi.
\v 17 Maraga mo tudori taligu mo vano Rama lo valena, me taie hi mo vevegi nire tau Israel. Me u vonda na vonda gogona noi \nd Huqe\nd*.
\c 8
\s1 Israel ram Tarani na Ratahigi
\p 
\v 1 Lo taro tavohe i Samuel u sesea, mo tau netune mwera gairue rom vuragi nora tangaloi vevegi tau Israel.
\v 2 I netune mwera togagi i Joel me henai netune tuegi su hurie i Abisa. Ngere rom voragi tangaloi vevegi lolo Bereseba.
\v 3 Siu renetune mwera rai dige tea lo nona turegi. Rau begi denie ram lai gineu lo turegi he vovohoi tea, me ram vevegi na tangaloi lo turegi he vovohoi tea.
\p 
\v 4 Siu sesea doluegi tau Israel ram galo bubugi, me ram vomai lobei Samuel lo Rama,
\v 5 me ram veve lawea vena, “Nigo gu sesea, me netumu mwera rohe dige tea lo nom turegi. Go rivu na nomai ratahigi nge vin vevegi gamai mwereire sinobu doluegi lolo vanue dolue.”
\v 6 Lo taro hi ram veve vena, “Go rivu na nomai ratahigi vin vevegi gamai,” Samuel he havuhevu tea. Siu mo tataro lawe \nd Huqe\nd*.
\p 
\v 7 Me \nd Huqe\nd* mo veve lawe Samuel vena, “Rorontagi na leora tangaloi doluegi ngerehi rain veve lawego. Hateve rau rahagi nigo, nge i neu hi ram rahagi eu hurive neu a nora ratahigi gorora.
\v 8 Mwere doluegi na doridori ngehi rau vei mo tavuigi lo rani hi nau lei vohogi nire dena Ijib me mo dadari bagataha. Ram siregi eu me ram tabana lawe huqe saosao wagineu, siu ngere ram vai mwerehi vage lawego.
\v 9 Me siserigi lehe go rorontagi na leora nge i nigo goin veve siagagi lawera. Me goin matamwasaragi lawera vena, havagineu hi nora ratahigi vin vei, tavohe vin leogorora, siu vin vei mwerehi mo lado hurive u vovohoi.”
\p 
\v 10 Me Samuel mo veve na leo noi \nd Huqe\nd* doluegi lawe na tangaloi ngerehi ram hui na ratahigi denie.
\p 
\v 11 Me mo veve vena, “Nge ngaha nge vin vuragi nomiu ratahigi, nge vin leogoro gimiu, vin vei mwerehi mo lado vena u vovohoi: renetumu mwera vin teure rain vuragi nona tangaloi jariot me tangaloi hosi. Me rain toa lo nagoi nona jariot\f + \fr 8.11 \ft A jariot a hosi mo revea a wiligi gairue. A tangaloi mo toa lune u siseri garagara.\f* doluegi.
\v 12 Nge vin rivure lalavasigi rain vuragi nona tomtomuegi nora teri vatusao, me tomtomuegi nora buri ngavulu gailime. Me vin taure lalavasigi rain geli momogagi nona tano, lalavasigi rain vile na gana hinaga matue. Taligu, lalavasigi rain vei na langoi vuro me lalangoi nona jariot.
\v 13 Me nge vin lei vohogi renetumiu vavine rain vuragi tangaloi vurei bonagi mwere digugu me rain vuragi tangaloi sasalawai me tangaloi quiqui.
\v 14 Ngeie vin lei vohogi na talumiu hi a gineu gagarea lolona, me dena talui bulemiu garo inuinu, siu dena talui oliv, go mo betera lawe na nona tangaloi tabana.
\v 15 Ngeie vin lei gategale den hangavulu lo bulemiu toli, me mwasi garo inuinu, go betera lawe na nona tangaloi gaihango me lawe na nona tangaloi tabana.
\v 16 Ngeie vin lei na nomiu tangaloi tabana mwera me a nomiu tangaloi tabana vavine, me a bulemiu bulugi gagarea mena bulemiu donki saosao, me ngeie vin tambara lo nona tabana.
\v 17 Ngeie vin lei gategale den hangavulu lo bulemiu nani, mena sibsib me gimiu nein vuragi nona tangaloi tabana.
\v 18 Lo rani hi gimiu nein ngara huri buluiana dein ratahigi ngehi neu teue, nge i \nd Huqe\nd* vin he duvi gimiu tea lo rani hi.”
\v 19 Ngere sinobu ram rao ve rain rorongtagi na leoi Samuel, me ram veve vena, “Hatie! Nge gamai gam tarani na ratahigi goro gamai.
\v 20 Siu gamai gain mwere na buri sinobu wagineu ve nomai ratahigi ngeie vin vevegi gamai me vin tomuegi gamai, me vin qalo nomai vuro.”
\v 21 Me Samuel mo rorongtagi na leo doluegi nora tangaloi, me mo valuhuri na leora lawe \nd Huqe\nd*.
\p 
\v 22 Siu \nd Huqe\nd* mo veve lawe Samuel vena, “Rorontagi nire me goin teu na nora ratahigi.”
\p Me Samuel mo veve lawera tau Israel vena, “Gimiu gagategalegi nein mule lo vanue miu.”
\c 16
\s1 \nd Huqe\nd* mo Vilewahe Devet mo vuragi na Ratahigi
\p 
\v 1 \nd Huqe\nd* mo veve lawe Samuel vena, “?Vi dadari tagaha nigo goin hahagavi huri Sol? Nge neu nau rahagi nie ve vin ratahigi goro Israel. Horongi na nom laha gena vurei me gom vano, nain hora go lawe Jesi, tangaloi tau Betlehem. Nau vilewahe netune gategale lawe au ve vin vuragi ratahigi.”
\p 
\v 2 Siu Samuel mo veve vena, “?Nain vano mwere hilogo? Tareve i Sol vin rongo au, vin ue vaga mate au.”
\p Me \nd Huqe\nd* mo veve vena, “Goin lei na bulugi mwane meigo me goin veve vena, ‘Neu nam vomai huri na hure bonboni\f + \fr 16.2 \ft Hure bonboni duvi lawe na \nd Huqe\nd* duvigi tangaloi mo gani. Mo eno vage lo varagi gai tolu me gai lime.\f* lawe\nd Huqe\nd*.’
\v 3 Me goin veve, i Jesi vin vomai lo hure bonboni me nai haharagi lawego havagi goin vei. Me goin sasavi na vurei gogona ngehinge lo tangaloi ngehi nain vevea lawego.”
\p 
\v 4 Siu Samuel mo vai mwere hi \nd Huqe\nd* u veve lawea. Mo vomai Betlehem, me ngere sesea tau lolo vanue renge ram matagu tavohe ram vano lobena. Me ram veve vena, “?Gom vomai mena tamwata?”
\p 
\v 5 Me Samuel duvi vena, “Neu nam vomai mena tamwata; huri na hure bonboni lawe \nd Huqe\nd*. Gimiu nein toga gogona, me nein vomai mei eu lo hure bonboni.” Siu ngeie mo vai gogonagi Jesi mei renetune mwera me nge mo veve lawera vena rain vomai lobena lo hure bonboni.
\p 
\v 6 Siu lo taro tavohe ram vomai me nge mo lehi Eliab me nge mo lado vena, “Io hogo, tangaloi ngehi \nd Huqe\nd* u vile wahea vena nai vureie nge lehe mo labe.”
\p 
\v 7 Nge \nd Huqe\nd* mo veve lawe Samuel vena, “Mese leo lo nagona me qaravune huri nau rahagi nie beno. Ba huri neu nam leo hateve mwere hi tangaloi mo leo. Tangaloi nge mo lehe lo tarabehine, nge neu nam leo lolo dinmwango na.”
\p 
\v 8 Siu Jesi mo ware Abinadab me mo vaie mo dige utu lo nagoi Samuel. Nge Samuel mo veve vena, “Taligu \nd Huqe\nd* nge he vile wahea tea.”
\v 9 Siu Jesi mo vai Sama mo dige utu lo nagoi Samuel, nge Samuel mo veve vena, “Taligu, \nd Huqe\nd* nge he vile wahea tea.”
\v 10 Me Jesi u vei netune mwera gaibitu ram dige utu lo nagoi Samuel, nge Samuel mo veve lawe Jesi vena, “\nd Huqe\nd* nge he vile wahera tea.”
\v 11 Me Samuel mo hui Jesi vena, “?Netumu ngere belehe?”
\p Me Jesi mo veve vena, “Tahigi redu mo tino mosigei. Mo leogoro na sibsib.”
\p Me Samuel mo veve lawea vena, “Go hora na tangaloi na vano hurie me na laie, huri nain toga tea vuine vin hurive da gagani vin dadari mo vomai talehe.”
\v 12 Siu Jesi mo hora na tangaloi mo vano hurie, me mo laie. Ngeie a vulune u memea, u garea tatarise, me mo gabisie.
\p Me \nd Huqe\nd*mo veve vena, “Ngeie hi, maraga gom sasavi na vurei gogona lune.”
\v 13 Me i Samuel mo lai na laha hi a vurei lolona mo vureie Devet lo livugei retuana. Siu siserigi hi a Vui noi \nd Huqe\nd* mo vomai lui Devet lo ranigi hi mo vano. Siu Samuel mo maraga mo vano Rama.
\c 17
\s1 ‫ Devet Mo Qaragi Kalaiot
\p 
\v 1 Siserigi hi ngere Balistaen mena nora tangaloi vuro vena rain qalo, me rau galo bubugi Soko lolo vanue Juda. Ram toga bubugi tahinge Damim lolo Ebes lo livugei Soko me na Aseka.
\v 2 Sol me i ngere Israel ram vumai bubugi lolo waluwelu tahinge Ela, me ramo tau vurugegi nire vena ran qalo meire tau Balistaen.
\v 3 Ngere Balistaen ramo labe lo vusi gategale lo tavului welu me ngere tau Israel ramo labe tavului vusi, me waluwelu lo mahogi lo livugara.
\p 
\v 4 Me a tangaloi huire gategale ngeie tau Kat, mo mwalue dena siusiu nora Balistaen, a henana i Kalaiot. Qaravune sugu gaiono dumu gategale.
\v 5 Me a gairoqoi qatune rau veie lo vatu meraga me gaitugoroi luqe mo luqegi nie lo betune a vatu meraga, a mavagi mwere na vatu wuwerigi teri vagalime.
\v 6 Gairoqoi garune rau veire lo vatu meraga, me a nona gaimenu rau veie lo vatu meraga mo sanga lo livugei siqana.
\v 7 Nona gaituru mwere na sili gamali, a qatugi aean a mavagi mo mwere na vatui woro ngavulu gairue domwa gailime. Tangaloi mo wali na nona gaisingi mo vano tomuegi nie.
\p 
\v 8 Kalaiot mo labe me mo waregi lawera ngere tau Israel. “Huri havai nem mai nem labegi vurugegi hurive da qalo? Hateve i neu tau Balistaen me gimiu tangaloi noi Sol? Nen vile wahe na tangaloi gategale na himei lobengu.
\v 9 Tarevena ngeie vin vei lei vena vin wehi eu nain mate, gamai gain voragi nomiu tangaloi tabanagi. Tarevena neu nain vei lei ve nain wehie vin mate, gimiu nein voragi nomai tangaloi tabanagi. Siu nein tabana nomai.”
\v 10 Me Kalaiot mo veve vena, “Lo rani lehe nam leo savi gimiu tangaloi vuro tau Israel! Ne bete lawe au a tangaloi goron vui ue.”
\v 11 Tavohe Sol ram rongo na leo noi tangaloi tau Balistaen hi, me ngere doluegi tau Israel ram matagu liu garagara me ram rongoe u esi garagara.
\p 
\v 12 Devet netui tangaloi gategale tau Evrat a henagi tuegi Betlehem lolo vanue Juda. Henai tamana i Jesi. Netune mwera ngere gaiwelu, me lolo taro noi Sol, i Jesi u sesea vohogi.
\v 13 Me netui Jesi gaitolu togagi rau vano ram huri Sol lolo vuro: Togagi henana i Eliab; su hurie i Abinadab; me gaitoligi i Sama.
\v 14 Devet ngeie a tahigi redu. Me retogana gaitolu rau huri Sol.
\v 15 Tuqaravu i Devet u tudori taligu dein Sol vena leogoro na sibsib bulei tamana Betlehem.
\v 16 Lolo rani ngavulugaivesi tangaloi tau Balistaen hinge mo vumai kakarani mo labe vataha robongi me revirevi.
\p 
\v 17 Me i Jesi mo veve lawe netune mweragi Devet vena, “Go lai na sasalawai ngere lehe me na bereti hangavulu ngere lehe siseri lawe retuemu ram toga bubugi lo tanoi vuro.
\v 18 Me siu go lai na utei hinaga ngere lehe hangavulu lawe na tomtomuegi nora u teri. Me goin lehi retuemu siu goin vumai taligu gom veve hurive wuraha meire.”
\v 19 Ngere tora Sol me na tangaloi ngere doluegi tau Israel lolo waluwelu hinge Ela, ram qalo meire tau Balistaen.
\p 
\v 20 Lolo robongi siaga Devet mo siregi na sibsib ta lo tanoi leohuri nora tangaloi leogoro sibsib, mo lai na hinaga me mo vano, mwere hi Jesi u dedegi. Ngeie u dadari lo tanogi hinge ram toga bubugi taie tavohe a tangaloi vuro ram ngarangaragi me ram vano ram lai tanora vena rain qalo.
\v 21 Me ngere tau Israel me ngere tau Balistaen ram labegi na vuro ram vui leoleo.
\v 22 I Devet u membu siregi na nona gineu ngere hi lobena tangaloi mo leogoro getei hinaga, mo toa mo vano lobera ram labegi vuro me mo hui retuana vena rau mwere hilogo.
\v 23 Me tavohe mo gato meire, Kalaiot, ngeie tau Balistaen a tangaloi gilu garea tau Kat, mo mwalue dena burigi me mo ngarangaragi siaga mwere hi tamwere me mo vaivei lolohaga, me i Devet mo rongoe.
\p 
\v 24 Tavohe tangaloi doluegi tau Israel ram lehi na tangaloi hinge, ngere ram toa denie me ngere ram matagu lawagi.
\v 25-26 Me ngerehi tau Israel ram veve vena, “Nem lehi na tangaloi mo tuhuri mo vumai. Ngeie mo vumai vena saogi nire tau Israel.” Me Devet mo hui dena tangaloi ram labe lobena vena, “?Havagineu i ratahigi vin vei lawe na tangaloi ngehi vin ue vagamate na tangaloi tau Balistaen hinge me vin lei vohogi na maleana lehe dena Israel? Tangaloi tau Balistaen lehe hateve rau tevegigilegi nie tea me ngeie a tangaloi vurogi. Ngeie u vei asisigi na henai tangaloi vuro noi Huqe Mauri Vagituei.” Me ngere ram veve vena, “I ratahigi vin bete na gineu gagarea lawe na tangaloi ngehi vin wehi na tangaloi lehe vin mate. Ngeie vin bete netune vavine vena vin legi meie me vin lei vohogi denie mei rehavana rain mese tuli homu lawe na ratahigi tau Israel.”
\v 27 Me ngere ram veve lawea vena, “Ngaha havagineu i ratahigi vin vei lawe na tangaloi hine hi vin wehie vin mate.”
\v 28 Me tavohe Eliab, i tuei Devet togagi, mo rongoe mo gato lawe na tangaloi, mo vaie Eliab a merona mo mwere na avi mo mui su lawe Devet. Me mo hui vena, “Huri na havagi gom himei talehe? Me gu teu na sibsib wewerigi ngerehi lawe hine lolo vanue vurogi? Nau iloe mwere hilogo a nomu sagesage mena domimu hinge asigi; gom vumai hogosie hurive gon leo vuro.”
\v 29 Devet mo veve vena, “Nau vei na havagi? Hurive neu nai mese gato?”
\v 30 Siu mo talele dori lawe na tangaloi dolue me mo veve na leo mwerehi teu, me tangaloi ngere ram duvi lawea mwere hi tomue.
\p 
\v 31 Me ngere ram rongo‪‬ na leoi Devet. Me ram veve serea lawe Sol, me i Sol mo hora hurie.
\v 32 Devet mo veve lawe Sol vena, “Dominde na mese soi lo valuhuri tangaloi lehe tau Balistaen; Nomu tangaloi tabanagi vin vano mo gilu meie.”
\v 33 Sol mo duvi, “Nigo goi vei telai vena goin vano goin gilu me na tangaloi lehe tau Balistaen; nigo a mwalagelo vohogi, me ngeie a tangaloi vuro tavohe mo mwalagelo tau mo dadari bagataha.”
\v 34 Nge i Devet mo veve lawe Sol vena, “Nomu tangaloi tabanagi mo leogoro sibsib bulei tamana. Tavohe a laion sige a bea mo mai vena wali vohogi na sibsib dena burigi,
\v 35 Nam hurie mo vano nam wehie me nam wali vohogi na sibsib dena singona. Me tavohe mo tudori huri eu, Nam wiri lo vulune me nam wehie mo mate.
\v 36 Ngere vunu a laion mena bea; Nom tangaloi tabanagi u ue vaga matera; Tangaloi lehe tau Balistaen hateve rau tevegigilegi nie siu vin mwere laion mena bea, ba huri mo vaivei lolohaga mena tangaloi vuro noi Huqe Mauri Vagituei.”
\v 37 Devet mo veve vena, “\nd Huqe\nd* ngehi u lei vohogi eu dena limei laion me dena limei bea ngeie vin lei vohogi eu dena limei tangaloi tau Balistaen.” Sol mo veve lawe Devet vena, “Go vano, me i \nd Huqe\nd* ngeie meigo.”
\v 38 Sol mo luqegi Devet gena luqana. Me mo tau na luqe gaitugoroi vuro lune me a gairoqoi qetu rau veie lo vatu meraga lo qatune.
\v 39 Me Devet mo vai raraie, buei vuro mo taue lolo luqana me mo dige samwegi, ba huri hateve u luqegi nire tau, ngeie mo veve lawe Sol vena, “Nain vano tea lai me na gineu ngere, ba huri neu hateve nau hangovire mosigei.” Siu ngeie mo lai vohogi nire.
\v 40 Me mo lai na nona gaitigo lo limana me mo vile na vatu gailime rau minu dena matewelu, mo taure lolo gete, mena nona talivava lo limana, me mo vano kakarani lobei Kalaiot.
\p 
\v 41 Siserigi lehe Kalaiot mo vumai huri Devet, me na tangaloi mo wali na gaisingi betune mo tomue.
\v 42 Tavohe i Kalaiot mo lehi Devet, me mo leosavie, mo lehie hurivena ngeie u biti dena maresu mwera, a vulune u memea mo gabisie.
\v 43 Kalaiot mo veve lawe Devet huri vena, “?Neu a wiriu huri gom vomai huri eu mena gai?” Me Kalaiot mo tagaroagi asisigi Devet lo henai nona huqe saosao.
\v 44 Me mo veve lawea vena, “Go vumai lobengu nain bete na tarabesi mu lawe na manu lolo mahava me lawe na kankarue tau lolo songo!”
\v 45 Me i Devet mo veve lawe Kalaiot vena, “Go vumai vovohi eu gena buei vuro me na gaituru mena gaimenu, nge i neu nain vomai vovohoi go lo henai \nd Huqe\nd* Managi, Huqe nora tangaloi vuro tau Israel ngeie hi gom vaivei lolohaga meie.
\v 46 Lo rani ngelehe i \nd Huqe\nd* vin bete go tau lolo limegu, me nain wehi go, goin taqao vuine me nain tei utu na qatumu. Lo rani ngelehe nain bete na betui tangaloi vuro tau Balistaen lawe na manu lolo mahava me lawe na kankarue tau lolo songo! Me lolo ureure doluegi rain iloe huri vena lolo Israel a nora Huqe Mauri lure.
\v 47 Tangaloi doluegi ram tino talehe. Siu rain iloe vena hateve gena buei vuro, sige a gaimenu, huri \nd Huqe\nd* ngeie a huireana vin qaragi na vuro lehe siu ngeie vin bete gimiu doluegi talolo lime mai.”
\p 
\v 48 Tavohe Kalaiot mo vano mo kakarani lobena vena wehie, Devet mo toa siseri suvovohoie vena ron gilu.
\v 49 Siu mo haga ta lolo nona gete mo roa na vatu, mo siugi nie mo hogo lo raei Kalaiot. A vatu hinge u soro ta lolo qatune, mo soi lo nagona sulo tano.
\v 50 Devet qaragi Kalaiot gena talivava me na vatu: Mo totogie mo soi ta vuine mo mate, hateve gina buei vuro lolo limei Devet.
\v 51 Devet mo toa mo labe gagaliue. Mo lai na nona buei vuro dena tanogi. Siu mo ue vagamatea, mo tai vohogi na qatune gena buei vuro noi Kalaiot sibona. Tavohe ngere tau Balistaen ram leo nora tangaloi huire u mate, ngere ramo tudori me ram toa.
\p 
\v 52 Siu ngere sinobu tau Israel me Juda ramo ngarangaragi vuro me ramo hurire ngere tau Balistaen mo dadari Kat me lo matai ara Ekron. Ram wehire ram vui mategi lo turegi mo vano Ekron mo dadari lo matai ara Ekron me Kat.
\v 53 Tavohe sinobu ngere tau Israel rau livusire tau Balistaen mo rovo, ram tudori vano ram wali vohogi na nora gineu doluegi.
\v 54 Devet mo lai na qatui tangaloi tau Balistaen me mo vano meie Jerusalem; mo tau na nona langoi vuro lolo nona vale siusiu.
\p 
\v 55 Tavohe i Sol mo lehi Devet mo vano lobei Kalaiot, ngeie mo veve lawe Abna tomtomuegi nora tangaloi tau lolo vuro vena, “?Netui hine mwalagelo mwera lehe?” Abna mo duvi lawea vena, “Mwere hi gom toga Ratahigi, neu nau haroe.”
\v 56 I Ratahigi mo veve vena, “Gon haqea huri vena, ‘?Netui hine mwalagelo mwera hinge?’”
\v 57 Tavohe Devet mo tudori u wehi Kalaiot, Abna mo laie mo vano meie lawe Sol, me a qatui Kalaiot hinge mo wiribibie tau lolo limana.
\v 58 Sol mo huie, “?Nigo netui hine mwalagelo mwera?” Devet mo veve vena, “Neu i netui ‬nom tangaloi tabanagi Jesi tau Betlehem.”
\c 22
\s1 Devet mo vano Adulam me Misba
\p 
\v 1 Devet mo siregi Kat mo salavohogi mo vano lolo malanga Adulam. Tavohe i retuana me i rehavai tamana lo vale ram rongo hurie, ngere ram hivo tahinge lombena.
\v 2 Ngere doluegi ram toga lo romasi me lavasigi a bugure lategi sige ram tarani na gineu hateve ram laie ram ara dalie, siu me mo voragi nora tomtomuegi. Lategi tangaloi vudolue vaga vesi ngere bulu.
\v 3 Tahinge Devet mo vano lo vanue renge hi Misba lolo Moab me mo veve lawe na ratahigi tau Moab vena, “Goin siregi lei vena i tamangu me i retahingu roin vumai roin tino lombemu vin dandari lune neu nain iloe vena havai hi Huqe vin vei laweau?”
\v 4 Siu ngeie mo siregi nire lombei ratahigi tau Moab, me ram tino ngere bulu tavohe Devet ngeie lolo ara tugoro.
\v 5 Maraga a tangaloi ligoligogi Kat mo veve lawe Devet vena, “Mese tino lolo ara tugoro. Go vano lolo vanue Juda.” Me i Devet mo siregi mo vano lolo tamatue i ute Heret. / Sol mo wehi na tangaloi toretore tau Nod
\s1 Sol move na wehi na tangaloi toretore ngere hi
\p 
\v 6 Siseri lehe i Sol mo rongo hurive i Devet mena nona tangaloi rau haqera. Siu i Sol, a gaimenu lolo limana, u toga lolo vavai gai a Tamaris lo vusi Kibea, mena nona tangaloi tambanagi doluegi ram lambe dalie.
\v 7 Sol mo veve lawera vena, “Nen rongo, gimiu ta Benseman! Netui Jesi vin bete talu ngere hi mena viniat lolona lawe gimiu? Ngeie vin vei gimiu doluegi nein voragi tomtomuegi nora teri mena tomtomuegi nora ngere vudolue?
\v 8 Ngehi havagi mo vaie gimiu doluegi nem qalo meieu? Hateve tangaloi gategale vena u veve laweau tavohe i netungu u vei na waratau siaga mei netui Jesi. Gimiu gategale hateve u romasi huri eu sige veve lawe au huri vena i netungu u veie a nongu tangaloi tambana mo taqao rarai eu, mwere hi mo vai bagataha.”
\v 9 Maraga i Doek tau Edom, ngeie mo lambe mena tangaloi tambana noi Sol, mo veve vena, “Neu nau lehi na maresu mwera netui Jesi u vumai lombei Ahimelek maresu mwera netui Ahitub Nob.
\v 10 Ahimelek mo hui dein MAURI hava gineu vin vei meie; me mo bete leo gaiture mena buei vuro noi Kalaiot tau Balistaen.”
\v 11 Me i ratahigi (Sol) mo hora huri na tangaloi toretore hi i Ahimelek netui Ahitub mei rehavai tamana doluegi, ngere a tangaloi toretore tau Nob, me ngere doluegi rau vumai lombei ratahigi.
\v 12 Sol mo veve vena, “Siseri hi go rorontagi, a maresu mwera netui Ahitub.” / ngeie mo duvi vena, “Io nongu mauri,”
\v 13 Sol mo veve lawea vena, “Huri na havai gom qalo meieu, ningo tomu netui Jesi, gom bete na bereti mena buei vuro me gom hui huri dein Huqe huri eu, siu huri vin qalo meieu me mo tagaragi eu me mo tino ragi eu, mwere hi mo vai bataha?”
\v 14 Ahimelek mo duvi lawe Sol vena, “Dena tangaloi nom tambanagi doluegi, hine hi u veve hogo mwerei Devet, ngehi i qeligei ratahigi, a tomtomuegi nomu matagoro rau lando mavagi nie lolo valemu?
\v 15 A rani lehe nam bei hui turegi lehe dein Huqe hurie? ngehi hatie! Mese siregi ratahigi mo qalo mei nom tangaloi tambana sige rehavai retamana, huri neu tangaloi nom tambanagi nahe ilo na havagi tea lolo gineu doluegi lehe.”
\v 16 Maraga i ratahigi mo veve vena, “Ningo goin mate hogo, Ahimelek, ningo mei rehavai tamamu doluegi.”
\v 17 Me i ratahigi mo veve lawe na nona tangaloi mo lambe lo mwararana: “Nen tudori me nem wehi na tangaloi toretore noi MAURI, ba ngere vage ram bulu lo tavalugi mei Devet. Ngere rau iloe vena mo salavohogi, siu me rahe veve serea tea laweau.” / Maraga tangaloi tambanagi noi ratahigi ram rongoe hateve u garea vena rain heu limara vena rain wehi na tangaloi toretore noi MAURI
\v 18 Ratahigi mo hora Doek, “Ningo go tudori vano me gom wehi na tangaloi toretore ngerehi.” Me Doek ngeie tau Edom mo tudori mo vili tulire. Lo ranigi hi ngeie u wehi na tangaloi ngavulu gaiwelu domwagi gailime ngere hi ram wali na ebhot.
\v 19 Me ngeie u teu na buei vuro vage Nod, a togagi venue nora tangaloi toretore ngere hi, meire mweragi mena vavinegi, a maresu mena maresu ngere hi ram titi teu, me bulugi, donki mena sibsib.
\v 20 Maraga i Abiata, a mwera netui Ahimelek a mwera netui Ahitub, u toa sasavohogi mo bulu mei Devet.
\v 21 Mo veve lawe Devet vena i Sol u wehi na tangaloi toretore noi MAURI.
\v 22 Siu i Devet mo veve lawe Abiata vena: “A rani hi, tavohe i Doek tau Edom ngeie tahinge, nau ilo vurugegi vena ngeie vin veve lawe Sol. Mateana noi rehavai tamamu doluegi mo eno laweau.
\v 23 Go tino lombengu; mese matagu; a tangaloi hi mo hingesi go ngeie mo hingesi eu vage. Ningo goin mwaso lo tanoi nongu leogoro.”
